title: Did Nancy Pelosi Routinely Use a ‘Big Fat 200-Seat Jet’ to Travel to California?
subtitle: Rumor claims Nancy Pelosi spurned use of the House Speaker's 'small private jet' and demanded it be replaced with a 'big fat 200-seat jet.'
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: House Speaker Nancy Pelosi routinely used a "big fat 200-seat jet" to travel between California and D.C.
